snippet.title: Home Minister Rajnath Singh Calls High Level Meeting On Uri Attacks

localized.description:
Home minister Rajnath Singh has called a high level meeting in North Block over the Uri attacks. Defense minister Manohar Parrikar will be present in the meeting.
